WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:01.787
Well, good evening, family.

00:00:01.787 --> 00:00:04.267
Thank you for joining us tonight.

00:00:04.267 --> 00:00:06.940
We're excited you're here, and I'm excited to be here.

00:00:06.940 --> 00:00:08.551
We have work to do.

00:00:09.227 --> 00:00:17.600
I've been going over some things that I could share with you today and what the Lord has been talking to me about over the last several days.

00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:31.120
I've been taking my time and not doing as many live streams because of what the Holy Spirit has been instructing me on.

00:00:31.867 --> 00:00:38.151
So, let me start off with this: He said, I want you to go back to the basics.

00:00:38.151 --> 00:00:42.537
I want you to go back to the foundations of where you came from.

00:00:42.537 --> 00:00:49.691
Don't forget where you came from; the books you've read, the things that have ministered to you, read them again.

00:00:49.691 --> 00:00:51.520
Go over them again.

00:00:51.520 --> 00:00:54.320
Faith cometh by hearing, and hearing by the word of God.

00:00:54.320 --> 00:00:57.954
And people that are more mature than you, you can learn from them.

00:00:57.954 --> 00:01:03.120
People that have been in ministry longer than you, you can learn from them.

00:01:03.120 --> 00:01:14.480
I don't know everything, of course, and being a newbie in this, I learn from people who have walked it longer than I have as far as ministry goes.

00:01:15.280 --> 00:01:17.820
It always goes back to this book.

00:01:18.090 --> 00:01:32.479
I know this isn't that old, but I don't even know this man, John Bevere, but The Awe of God has changed our life.

00:01:33.359 --> 00:01:39.529
I'm telling you, I look forward to my wife reading me this book.

00:01:39.529 --> 00:01:41.760
She reads it to me every day.

00:01:41.760 --> 00:01:46.020
We go over the chapters and she highlights and marks it all up.

00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:54.640
Then she found out that there are YouTube videos that talk about each chapter that John Bevere wrote.

00:01:54.880 --> 00:02:02.022
So we listen to it, and we go over it again, and we talk about it where we are in ministry.

00:02:02.410 --> 00:02:14.110
I've always said the first three chapters, you know, because I feel like if I can just get you to read part of it, if it ministers to Diana and me so much, I pray that it would minister to you.

00:02:14.400 --> 00:02:17.280
I don't recommend stuff very easily.

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:32.720
I don't believe in selling books a lot unless the Holy Spirit has led you to, but this book right here, I'm going to tell you, it has changed my life.

00:02:33.248 --> 00:02:39.505
I cannot wait until he has a new book on March 3rd.

00:02:39.920 --> 00:02:43.440
It's about Jesus's return.

00:02:43.440 --> 00:02:51.680
Now, Diana said he made the comment that everything that he's preached up until now has changed or something like that.

00:02:52.533 --> 00:02:57.440
I hope, you know, I don't know what that means, so I'm not going to add to it or take away from it.

00:02:58.800 --> 00:03:08.560
But I want to say this: this book, sir, I don't know if you watch our broadcast, but I'm going to tell you, you got an A+ from me on this one.

00:03:10.239 --> 00:03:15.173
Not that that matters, but it does to me and my wife.

00:03:15.991 --> 00:03:21.253
Chapter 12, 13, 14 is probably some of the most important chapters.

00:03:21.253 --> 00:03:24.709
I told Diana, I said, I read over them and read over them.

00:03:24.709 --> 00:03:39.920
There are times whenever I do these live streams and the presence of the Lord is so thick in my house, and there's so much chatter on the live stream.

00:03:40.613 --> 00:03:44.319
He has a quote right here that I thought was really beautiful.

00:03:44.319 --> 00:03:55.240
Here is the bottom line, the truth: Where the Lord is reverenced, His presence manifests.

00:03:55.240 --> 00:03:56.720
I've thought about that a lot.

00:04:00.613 --> 00:04:01.320
If we reverence Him, He manifests.

00:04:07.440 --> 00:04:38.150
The fear of the Lord is the beginning of wisdom, but the awe of Him, the reverence—there's so much that I could pull out of this, and I could have Diana read these highlights of all these underlying things, we'd be here all night, but there's so much of this book that I don't know how else to describe it to you.

00:04:41.184 --> 00:04:46.520
Like I said, I don't sell or push books.

00:04:46.520 --> 00:04:47.319
I don't do that.

00:04:47.519 --> 00:05:03.433
I have everybody and their brother trying to give me their book to push on my channel, but I'm going to tell you, he's never talked to me and I've never talked to him, but this book has blessed me.

00:05:03.433 --> 00:05:12.760
So, she read it to me most of the day going over these chapters just because I don't want to get off track.

00:05:13.600 --> 00:05:22.080
There's so much that the Lord, as I was ministering, praying over our house and praying over things.

00:05:22.080 --> 00:05:27.546
Last night He visited me for 45 minutes.

00:05:27.546 --> 00:05:33.830
He spoke to me about the future.

00:05:33.840 --> 00:05:40.320
It was the most intimate conversation I've had with Him in a long time.

00:05:40.320 --> 00:05:47.120
This was when He visited here and talked about President Trump; it was spectacular, it was amazing.

00:05:47.120 --> 00:05:57.430
But last night was just a friend instructing me about the ministry and about what we're doing.

00:05:58.144 --> 00:06:09.280
I fear Him, not scared; I reverence Him with this holy awe, the awe of God.

00:06:09.280 --> 00:06:20.720
When I tell you what I'm about to talk about a little bit tonight, asking about why you haven't come yet—what are you waiting on?

00:06:20.720 --> 00:06:27.919
With all the things we see in the earth right now, what is it that you're waiting on?

00:06:27.919 --> 00:06:35.760
Why haven't things escalated like a lot of you have always done?

00:06:35.760 --> 00:06:38.183
Brandon, He should come back tomorrow, He should come back today.

00:06:38.183 --> 00:06:39.554
Oh, Jesus is coming.

00:06:39.897 --> 00:06:42.100
I believe that with all my heart.

00:06:42.100 --> 00:06:47.039
But what are we waiting on?

00:06:48.173 --> 00:06:52.710
He gave me scripture.

00:06:52.720 --> 00:07:00.070
He gave me James 5:7.

00:07:02.479 --> 00:07:08.080
Be patient, therefore, brethren, until the coming of the Lord.

00:07:08.080 --> 00:07:27.840
Behold, the husbandman waiteth for the precious fruit of the earth, and hath long patience for it, until he receives the early and the latter rain.

00:07:27.840 --> 00:07:32.309
That's in the New Testament.

00:07:48.811 --> 00:08:03.919
He said to me, I told you, you're—this is amazing.

00:08:03.919 --> 00:08:10.879
You're not waiting on me, I'm waiting on you.

00:08:10.879 --> 00:08:18.479
Bring in my harvest, for the harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few.

00:08:18.479 --> 00:08:21.760
I'm waiting on my treasure, my harvest.

00:08:21.760 --> 00:08:26.062
Brandon, I'm leaving the 99 to go after the one.

00:08:26.062 --> 00:08:27.129
How many times?

00:08:27.129 --> 00:08:33.849
Until He showed me that verse, the Lord of the harvest.

00:08:33.849 --> 00:08:35.893
He came to me and had holes in His hands.

00:08:35.893 --> 00:08:37.199
He said, I died for all of you.

00:08:37.199 --> 00:08:39.839
Help me bring them in.

00:08:39.839 --> 00:08:43.039
I've given you the farming equipment.

00:08:43.039 --> 00:08:48.240
The vast fields of harvest are plentiful, Brandon.

00:08:48.240 --> 00:08:49.884
Do you see the harvest?

00:08:49.884 --> 00:08:53.760
Help me bring in the harvest.

00:08:53.760 --> 00:08:55.067
I died for every one of them.

00:08:55.067 --> 00:08:56.700
He held out His hands.

00:08:56.700 --> 00:08:58.320
He had humongous holes.

00:08:58.320 --> 00:09:00.720
They went right here.

00:09:01.086 --> 00:09:02.913
It wasn't in the middle.

00:09:02.913 --> 00:09:05.360
It was right here.

00:09:05.360 --> 00:09:07.234
A massive hole.

00:09:08.840 --> 00:09:10.730
It went clear into His palm right here.

00:09:10.730 --> 00:09:13.180
It was a massive hole.

00:09:13.180 --> 00:09:15.600
It wasn't in the center of His hand.

00:09:15.600 --> 00:09:17.138
It was right in here.

00:09:17.547 --> 00:09:22.800
I want to tell you that hole is massive.

00:09:22.800 --> 00:09:25.099
It took up the whole bottom half of His hand.

00:09:25.099 --> 00:09:33.910
You can see right through it to see the wheat bowing down before Him as He walked by it.

00:09:33.920 --> 00:09:35.060
One last call.

00:09:35.060 --> 00:09:39.279
He said, The sun is setting on this dispensation of grace.

00:09:39.279 --> 00:09:59.990
If anybody remembers that visitation that I had and I saw the sun setting and it was lowered down, and He stood there with His priestly robe, and He kept His voice turned into a shofar and He started saying, One last call.

00:10:00.251 --> 00:10:04.640
He started screaming and it echoed through the valley, One last call.

00:10:05.120 --> 00:10:12.036
He was calling for the sheep, and there were all these sheep, all different kinds, and I told you all about it.

00:10:12.036 --> 00:10:23.360
Then I saw the Father standing, and I saw Jesus at the hoopa, and it was olive leaf, and it was cut out, and it was the most beautiful thing.

00:10:23.600 --> 00:10:32.269
He was waiting on the bride, and I asked the Lord then, again, He said, You're not waiting on me, I'm waiting on you.

00:10:32.269 --> 00:10:37.110
Bring in my harvest, and I'll come and get you.

00:10:37.120 --> 00:10:41.920
There's no urgency in the church for the second coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:10:41.920 --> 00:10:45.760
There's not enough anticipation.

00:10:45.760 --> 00:10:55.947
A lot of people, we've become so dull and desensitized to the hearing of it that it's become just something we throw around.

00:10:55.947 --> 00:10:58.240
Jesus is coming.

00:10:58.240 --> 00:11:08.400
But the urgency of the hour and the expectation of it, we've become weary and wallowing, a lot of you.

00:11:08.400 --> 00:11:09.954
Oh, I have heard that.

00:11:10.366 --> 00:11:18.240
Brandon, you say that all the time, but I say it because it is real to me.

00:11:18.240 --> 00:11:27.600
And I yell it as loud as I can like John the Baptist, one crying in the wilderness, telling you, Jesus is coming.

00:11:27.600 --> 00:11:37.120
He is here, as the prophets of old cried out and warned that there was a king coming.

00:11:37.120 --> 00:11:39.839
Isaiah, all of them.

00:11:39.839 --> 00:11:44.389
How many times have we heard it?

00:11:44.399 --> 00:12:01.680
I want to be so sober to bring sobriety to you, to shake you, to waken you, to tell you again that our King is coming.

00:12:29.733 --> 00:12:31.680
It is not something that your grandma told you.

00:12:52.250 --> 00:12:52.480
I am being for real.

00:12:52.480 --> 00:12:56.142
Jesus is coming, but He is waiting for the fruit.

00:12:56.142 --> 00:12:57.209
James 5:7.

00:12:57.209 --> 00:13:03.200
If you need to hear it again, I will read it to you again.

00:13:17.920 --> 00:13:18.210
That is what He is waiting on.

00:13:19.080 --> 00:13:19.370
The fruit.

00:13:26.686 --> 00:13:26.937
The harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few.

00:13:26.937 --> 00:13:30.079
Bring in my harvest.

00:13:30.079 --> 00:13:38.696
This is where He was at as He talked to me last night.

00:13:38.696 --> 00:13:47.440
There are a lot of things He said I cannot talk about on your platform.

00:13:49.726 --> 00:13:51.440
It was just friend talk.

00:13:55.600 --> 00:14:02.870
He is my friend and I respect what He asked me to say.

00:14:02.880 --> 00:14:04.000
Therefore, do you have it?

00:14:04.000 --> 00:14:11.950
Be patient, brethren, until the coming of the Lord.

00:14:11.950 --> 00:14:18.217
See how the farmer waits for the precious fruit of the earth.

00:14:20.190 --> 00:14:20.650
It is the New King James Version.

00:14:20.650 --> 00:14:29.240
In the King James Version, be patient, therefore, brethren, until the coming of the Lord.

00:14:29.240 --> 00:14:38.959
Behold, the husbandman waiteth for the precious fruit of the earth and hath long patience.

00:14:55.333 --> 00:14:55.720
That means He is not in a hurry.

00:14:55.720 --> 00:15:02.540
He has long patience for it until He receives the early and the latter rain.

00:15:02.540 --> 00:15:05.199
He wants a major harvest.

00:15:05.199 --> 00:15:06.700
Can these bones live?

00:15:06.700 --> 00:15:10.568
That is what He was talking to me about, the harvest again.

00:15:10.568 --> 00:15:22.720
He said, There are so many that I cannot trust with the finances to get it done.

00:15:22.720 --> 00:15:32.285
He said, They will receive the money and do something else with it when I had an assignment for it.

00:15:32.285 --> 00:15:40.747
He said, Brandon, I will entrust you with much if you do not touch what is mine.

00:15:40.747 --> 00:15:53.653
Ministries, there are a lot of them that touch what is mine, and it is for the harvest.

00:16:09.053 --> 00:16:09.546
He said, I will give you yours and bless you, but keep the main thing the main thing.

00:16:09.546 --> 00:16:13.567
Do not touch what is mine.

00:16:13.567 --> 00:16:34.944
He said, There are a lot of ministers, Brandon, that do not do right with the money in the ministry, and I cannot trust them to get it done.

00:16:37.264 --> 00:16:41.360
I need buildings for my people for what is about to happen.

00:16:50.610 --> 00:16:50.980
I need land bought.

00:16:50.980 --> 00:17:03.910
But they will not do what I have asked them to do with it.

00:17:03.920 --> 00:17:06.959
They will be held accountable.

00:17:06.959 --> 00:17:18.559
As I was sitting there, I do not give any glory to the devil at all.

00:17:25.110 --> 00:17:26.680
I never talk about the devil or demons unless I feel instructed to, and tonight I do.

00:17:27.980 --> 00:17:42.800
I think a lot of things that Hollywood has, like Star Wars and other movies, they get the ideas from what they have seen in the demonic and they project it to you so you become desensitized.

00:17:53.080 --> 00:17:53.509
But as I was sitting there, the Lord said, I am going to allow you to see this again.

00:17:53.939 --> 00:17:57.600
I had forgotten about this, but He called them watchers.

00:17:57.600 --> 00:17:59.200
They looked like cats.

00:17:59.200 --> 00:18:01.911
They looked like the Black Panther movie.

00:18:01.911 --> 00:18:06.800
They had slight slit eyes, but they were glowing.

00:18:06.800 --> 00:18:10.080
They had a pad and they were writing down everything I was saying.

00:18:15.552 --> 00:18:16.735
I said, Lord, what are You allowing me to see that for?

00:18:28.613 --> 00:18:28.826
What is that?

00:18:28.826 --> 00:18:33.159
He said, They do not know what is coming.

00:18:33.159 --> 00:18:40.470
They do not know what I am about to do until I tell My prophetic voices in this earth.

00:18:40.470 --> 00:18:47.458
So they watch to see what is relayed, what you say.

00:18:47.458 --> 00:18:51.848
They do not know His next move because they are not intimate with Him.

00:18:51.848 --> 00:18:55.180
They are the ones that were cast out of heaven.

00:18:55.180 --> 00:19:03.160
Remember, they were watching and they were writing down everything they could to true prophetic voices that they knew were accurate.

00:19:11.520 --> 00:19:22.800
I am just telling you what I saw and what the Lord said.

00:19:24.462 --> 00:19:26.780
I do not look at Brandon Biggs as anything.

00:19:34.320 --> 00:19:36.290
I want everything to deflect to Him.

00:19:36.290 --> 00:19:43.040
They were taking note of things that I was saying privately.

00:19:46.346 --> 00:19:52.840
He said, There are certain things now that I will say to you that I do not want spoken out that you will hold.

00:19:57.440 --> 00:20:09.413
But because I said in My word that I do nothing in this earth unless I reveal it to My prophets first, I go by what I told and I stand by what I said I would do.

00:20:09.413 --> 00:20:14.754
Does that make sense, son?

00:20:14.754 --> 00:20:21.656
I do not want to add to or take away from anything my Son writes down.

00:20:28.320 --> 00:20:38.240
As I was in this moment, I realized the power and the authority of the believer and the words that He gives us, how important it is that we only say what He tells us to say.

00:20:38.240 --> 00:20:48.799
There have been times in this last couple of weeks that He has been silent and I have been like, What is wrong?

00:20:52.368 --> 00:20:52.944
What is going on?

00:21:12.060 --> 00:21:12.330
He said to me, The reason I am silent, there is a purpose for it.

00:21:12.330 --> 00:21:19.979
I only tell you what you need to hear when I need you to say it.

00:21:33.360 --> 00:21:33.720
If I am silent, it is not that I am angry.

00:21:33.720 --> 00:21:36.053
I go, Are we cool?

00:21:36.053 --> 00:21:37.588
Are we all right?

00:21:52.304 --> 00:21:52.848
What is going on?

00:21:52.848 --> 00:22:04.171
Because we have these conversations, but it is not instruction for the channel and for the people.

00:22:04.171 --> 00:22:10.300
He said, If I am quiet, I am quiet on purpose.

00:22:10.300 --> 00:22:12.182
I have nothing to say.

00:22:12.182 --> 00:22:14.180
Do you speak for Me?

00:22:14.180 --> 00:22:17.900
You do not speak for yourself, do you?

00:22:28.592 --> 00:22:28.976
I said, No.

00:22:33.600 --> 00:22:37.319
So, if I do not say nothing, that means I have nothing to say.

00:22:37.319 --> 00:22:38.354
It is not personal.

00:22:38.354 --> 00:22:39.005
Grow up.

00:22:45.862 --> 00:22:46.273
Go back to what I told you to do in the first place.

00:22:46.273 --> 00:22:47.096
Pray.

00:22:47.096 --> 00:22:51.347
You do not have to have a new vision.

00:22:51.347 --> 00:23:04.731
He said, Brandon, I can give you one thing, one vision to pray about on that channel, and you take that assignment and pray over it for months.

00:23:07.097 --> 00:23:16.746
I have given you a lot of stuff to bring to the people that they could intercede for, for the nations, for the harvest.

00:23:16.746 --> 00:23:27.662
If they will learn who they are in their authority and use their authority over their area, it would help.

00:23:27.662 --> 00:23:33.386
It is according to the word when it says that Satan has blinded the eyes of the unbeliever.

00:23:33.386 --> 00:23:36.440
He has blinded their eyes.

00:23:36.440 --> 00:23:40.880
But we take authority as believing believers and use our authority over the devil.

00:23:54.777 --> 00:23:55.005
We have power and authority over him to break off those chains that bind all of our unsaved loved ones and the eyes that are fogged.

00:23:55.005 --> 00:23:57.919
According to Ephesians 1, let the eyes of their understanding be enlightened.

00:23:57.919 --> 00:24:09.600
How much Jesus loves them.

00:24:09.600 --> 00:24:10.120
Paraphrase.

00:24:10.120 --> 00:24:28.710
How much God loves them.

00:24:28.720 --> 00:24:41.485
Let the eyes of their understanding be enlightened.

00:24:41.943 --> 00:24:59.626
What are they being enlightened to?

00:25:16.400 --> 00:25:22.235
That Jesus has a plan for their life.

00:25:22.235 --> 00:25:35.229
Beloved, I wish above all things that you prosper and be in health even as your soul prospers.

00:25:35.229 --> 00:25:35.825
Overflow.

00:25:35.825 --> 00:25:39.420
God is a God of overflow.

00:25:39.420 --> 00:25:44.503
Abundance to the full, to the extreme, to it overflows.

00:25:44.503 --> 00:25:53.600
He wants you to live a good life, healed and whole and delivered by the power of the Lord Jesus Christ, what He did for you.

00:25:53.600 --> 00:25:57.076
As He is, so are we in this world.

00:25:57.076 --> 00:26:00.149
Brandon, just go back to the fundamentals.

00:26:00.149 --> 00:26:01.739
Keep praying.

00:26:22.844 --> 00:26:23.013
If I do not give you a new word, go back to the things you consider old.

00:26:23.013 --> 00:26:24.015
They are not old.

00:26:24.015 --> 00:26:25.004
Nothing is old.

00:26:30.632 --> 00:26:30.944
It is still new.

00:26:31.568 --> 00:27:10.000
But go back to the things I have told you and pray over them, especially with what I have seen concerning Iran and the president and what we are going to do to pray over President Trump and his protection and pray over his family and pray over our nation for the decisions that will be made with the Supreme Court concerning the tariffs in the next couple of weeks.

00:27:10.000 --> 00:27:14.914
Whenever they come back, I believe it was February 20th.

00:27:14.914 --> 00:27:24.399
They come back from their winter recess, so we pray over that.

00:27:24.399 --> 00:27:26.994
Praying over this decision whenever they go into Ramadan.

00:27:46.280 --> 00:27:46.560
I believe Ramadan starts this Wednesday.

00:27:46.840 --> 00:27:52.149
I am praying for the greatest harvest of souls in the Muslim community we have ever seen.

00:27:53.760 --> 00:28:01.215
God does not want anyone to perish, but all to come to repentance.

00:28:13.634 --> 00:28:14.320
I want to show you what is happening right now in New York.

00:28:14.320 --> 00:28:16.780
Congress is on recess until February 23rd, 2026.

00:28:18.129 --> 00:28:27.247
I want to show you the urgency of the hour and the major shaking that is about to awaken this nation.

00:28:45.172 --> 00:28:45.546
The Lord said, I am going to bring a shaking to awaken.

00:29:02.039 --> 00:29:02.586
I have seen all these major events and buildings on the 41st floor in Chicago on the riverfront and the hotels.

00:29:02.586 --> 00:29:05.430
Look, this is New York.

00:29:10.799 --> 00:29:10.977
It does not matter to me.

00:29:10.977 --> 00:29:12.221
They are all the trash.

00:29:12.221 --> 00:29:13.978
That is a call to prayer.

00:29:16.640 --> 00:29:17.959
A Muslim call to prayer all throughout New York.

00:29:17.959 --> 00:29:25.010
They voted for it.

00:29:25.010 --> 00:29:35.533
Are they shocked they got what they voted for?

00:29:35.533 --> 00:29:38.560
That should make believers mad.

00:29:38.560 --> 00:29:46.389
What are we doing?

00:30:04.470 --> 00:30:08.520
You can stop it.

00:30:11.760 --> 00:30:13.440
I do not want to hear that anymore.

